516
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:04,000
 So what is ALVA?

517
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:09,000
 ALVA is a series of interactive sessions exploring the basics of the Christian faith.

518
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:15,000
 In each session, you eat food, listen to a talk, and have discussions in small groups.

519
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:20,000
 Eating food together creates space for people to connect, relax, and build friendships.

520
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:25,000
 The talks tackle core questions about life and faith from a Christian perspective.

521
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:31,000
 And the discussion allows people to unpack these ideas without fear of being corrected or judged.

522
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:34,000
